INSTALL file for RCHIP Android Application
==========================================

From TARBALL
============

adb install rchip_android.apk
ADB is part of the android platform tools
get ADB from:
http://developer.android.com/sdk/index.html 
and follow the steps at the bottom

From Source
===========

If you plan on building from scratch and hacking this application
you need to have installed Eclipse(http://www.eclipse.org/) with ADT installed
(http://developer.android.com/sdk/eclipse-adt.html)


